# Installing {{.Name}}

## From Source

```sh
git clone {{.Module}}
cd {{.Name}}
task build
```

## Go

```sh
go install {{.Module}}@latest
```

## npm

```sh
npm install -g {{.Name}}
```

## pip

```sh
pip install {{.Name}}
```

## Homebrew

```sh
brew install {{.Name}}
```

## Verify Installation

```sh
{{.Name}} --version
```

## System Requirements

- Go 1.22+ (for Go builds)
- Node.js 20+ (for TypeScript builds)
- Python 3.11+ (for Python builds)
